Package: Kdirectional
Type: Package
Title: Analysis of anisotropy in point patterns using second order statistics
Version: 1.8-1
Date: 2022-12-15
Author: Tuomas Rajala
Maintainer: Tuomas Rajala <tuomas.rajala@iki.fi>
Description: Tools for analysing linear transformations of 2D and 3D point
    patterns. Includes various directed summary statistics, and scaling+rotation estimations
    using Fry points.
License: GPL
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 3.5.0),
    Rcpp (>= 0.10.6)
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Suggests:
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    spatstat
Imports: 
    graphics,
    grDevices,
    methods,
    utils,
    stats,
    Matrix,
    mvtnorm,
    rgl,
    sp
VignetteBuilder: knitr
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
URL: https://antiphon.github.io/Kdirectional/,
    https://github.com/antiphon/Kdirectional/
